Title: Crocodile 2: Death Swamp
Writer: Jace Anderson (screenplay), Boaz Davidson (story), Adam Gierasch (screenplay)
Actors: Heidi Lenhart, Chuck Walczak, Jon Sklaroff, Darryl Theirse
Plot: A criminal carrying stolen money and gold hijacks a plane that crashes in a Mexican swamp, where the survivors are terrorized by a giant crocodile.
